{"id":732,"date":"2020-10-07T16:04:31","date_gmt":"2020-10-07T16:04:31","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/?p=732"},"modified":"2020-10-07T16:38:34","modified_gmt":"2020-10-07T16:38:34","slug":"balancing-update-07-07-20","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/2020\/10\/07\/balancing-update-07-07-20\/","title":{"rendered":"Balancing Update (07\/10\/20)"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>We have made some modifications since our last few blog posts to Grothurn, Nephelinis and Freya based on feedback from the community.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The changes below are already live in-game &#8211; a restart of the app is required to get these modifications.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"\/>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>ZABAVA UPDATE<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>We are aware of a bug that has occurred as a result of a fix that reduced Zabava&#8217;s Speed stat from 27 to 18. This is <strong>not<\/strong> intentional, and this issue will be fixed, returned to 27, and live in-game tomorrow 8th October.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"\/>\n\n\n\n<p>The new Divine Titans are almost here, and thanks to the tireless work of our SPPs, YouTubers and development team, we have made some modifications to these Titans\u2019 skills before their launch this Friday 9th October.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The skills outlined in <strong><span class=\"has-inline-color has-vivid-green-cyan-color\">GREEN<\/span><\/strong> have been changed\/added:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"672\" height=\"473\" src=\"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/GrothurnUpdate-1.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-736\" srcset=\"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/GrothurnUpdate-1.png 672w, https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/GrothurnUpdate-1-300x211.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 672px) 100vw, 672px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Grothurn<\/strong> is intended to be a strong, spell-casting, defensive Titan. The following changes were made to improve this capability:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>His <strong>Counter<\/strong> ability was not working as intended, with some Spells failing to be cast &#8211; this has now been fixed.<\/li><li>We have added an additional <strong>+200% Titan &amp; Troop Health<\/strong> into his 1st Skill<\/li><li>Grothurn already had <strong>+30% Titan &amp; Troop All Elemental Resist<\/strong> in his 5th Skill, but this was not shown in the previous blog post.<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"672\" height=\"491\" src=\"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/NephelinisUpdate.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-734\" srcset=\"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/NephelinisUpdate.png 672w, https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/NephelinisUpdate-300x219.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 672px) 100vw, 672px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Nephelinis<\/strong> is intended to be an attacking force to be reckoned with, so the following changes have been made to reinforce this:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Nephelinis\u2019 1st Skill now casts <strong>Rage and Haste<\/strong> on 5 Allied Grenadiers every 15 seconds, whereas before these Grenadiers only gained Haste.<\/li><li>At Prestige Lvl10, Nephelinis will now call in <strong>3 Fire Elementals<\/strong> instead of 2 &#8211; this is to further improve their ability to act as a shield for the Titan and Grenadiers.<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"\/>\n\n\n\n<p>In addition to the Divine Titans, we\u2019ve also added a new skill to <strong>Freya\u2019s<\/strong> repertoire in order to better equip her for defensive play (in <strong><span class=\"has-inline-color has-vivid-green-cyan-color\">GREEN<\/span><\/strong>) &#8211; she will be available on SPP test accounts later today:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"672\" height=\"355\" src=\"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/FreyaUpdate.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-735\" srcset=\"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/FreyaUpdate.png 672w, https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/FreyaUpdate-300x158.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 672px) 100vw, 672px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Thanks again to our community and SPPs for trialing these Titans and we hope you look forward to Freya\u2019s Alliance War starting tomorrow, followed by the launch of the new Divine Sorcerers on Friday 9th October.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"\/>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>DOT CONTENT CREATORS:<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Whilst you wait for the Livestream\u2019s return, go check out some of the great DoT content creators and streamers across YouTube! Click the link on their names to go to their channels, and <strong>hit that subscribe button<\/strong> to get their latest videos as they drop:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/channel\/UCwS8gWrU26mj_C8DlwK_0WA\">ChefBaseGod<\/a> &#8211; Long time player and Discord-er returns with new content.<\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/user\/churritto19\/videos\">_Churro_<\/a> &#8211; Live streams, update videos and after-show gatherings.<\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/channel\/UC5S1d6IYSrt95MLKy4ITmMQ\/featured\">F2P Zeus<\/a> &#8211; Reactions, updates, battles, player profiles, Titan and Relic reviews.<\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/channel\/UCJ9s6BIyM7uUPJVAk7nbonw\">Vintage Plays<\/a> &#8211; DoT community conversations, overviews and streams.<\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/user\/TheMonkeygrl\">Dee NTG<\/a> &#8211; Insights from